sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Learning Interface
  participant AC as Adaptive Controller
  participant AE as AI Engine
  participant DB as Database System

  UI->>AC: completeSession()
  AC->>AE: getSessionAccuracy()
  Note over AE: Calculate performance metrics<br/>from session data
  AC->>AE: generateFeedback(topic)
  AC->>AE: getLearningAnalytics()
  Note over AE: Generate personalized insights<br/>recommendations, achievements
  AC->>AC: calculateNextDifficulty(currentLevel, accuracy)
  Note over AC: Apply progression rules<br/>based on performance thresholds
  AC->>AE: setNextSessionDifficulty(nextLevel)
  AC-->>UI: sessionSummary {feedback, analytics, progression}
  
  UI->>DB: updateTopicProgress(student_id, topic_id, session_data)
  Note over DB: Update cumulative statistics<br/>and learning history
  
  UI->>UI: Update local storage backup
  UI-->>UI: Display results with analytics<br/>and difficulty progression
